thread.title: BRIEF-Webstep ASA ‍Q4 EBITDA Ex-Items Down At NOK 19.5 Million

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Webstep ASA ‍Q4 EBITDA Ex-Items Down At NOK 19.5 Million
text:
Feb 15 (Reuters) - Webstep Asa:
* ‍TO PROPOSE A DIVIDEND OF NOK 1.50 PER SHARE​ * ‍BOARD TO PROPOSE A DIVIDEND OF NOK 1.50 PER SHARE, IN UPPER RANGE OF DIVIDEND POLICY.​
* ‍CONSOLIDATED REVENUES IN Q4 OF 2017 OF NOK 165.9 MILLION, UP 10.7 PER CENT FROM CORRESPONDING QUARTER LAST YEAR​
* ‍Q4 EBITDA EXCLUDING NON-RECURRING ITEMS WAS NOK 19.5 MILLION COMPARED TO NOK 20.7 MILLION LAST YEAR​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
